    <p>Prompt and effective care for common infections, ensuring your swift recovery. </p>

    <h3>Wound Dressing</h3>

    <p>Our expert wound care team provides meticulous dressing changes for optimal healing. </p>

    <h3>Antenatal Care for Women</h3>

    <p>Comprehensive prenatal care to support the health of expectant mothers and their babies.</p>

    <h3>Suturing and Removal of Sutures</h3>

    <p>Skilled suturing techniques and gentle removal of sutures for wound closure and healing. </p>

    <h3>Blood Cultures and Sputum Cultures</h3>

    <p>Precise diagnostic procedures to identify and treat infections effectively, improving your overall health and well-being. </p>



</div>
